mon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon I</a> (233)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys III</a> (283–298)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys I</a> (298–Present)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(Young_Griff)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (Young Griff)\">Aegon VI</a> (300–Present)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">Baratheons</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly I</a> (298–299)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis I</a> (299–Present)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Bastard pretenders</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gaemon_Palehair\" title=\"Gaemon Palehair\">Gaemon Palehair</a> (130)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Trystane_Truefyre\" title=\"Trystane Truefyre\">Trystane Truefyre</a> (130)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hammer\" title=\"Hugh Hammer\">Hugh Hammer</a> (130)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Blackfyre pretenders</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul>